  <T n="name">0xFE1C4AF6<!--Welcome to Nordhaven--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_World_Slide1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:19cb7364b514b9b0</T>
      <T n="text">0xF90C357A<!--Discover the enchanting beauty of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Nordhaven</font></b>, a northern coastal city where every season paints the landscape with unique scenic views. This vibrant world is alive with thriving, independent <b><font color='#199C2C'>Businesses</font></b> and a community spirit that will capture your heart.\n\nAt the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Nordhaven Train Station</font></b>, Sims can embark on new journeys or enjoy the passing trains.\nOr your Sims can explore the scenic canals, where they can help improve the environment and reveal hidden treasures.\n\nWhether you're here to make your mark in business or simply explore, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Nordhaven</font></b> offers endless opportunities.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_World_Slide2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:19cb7364b514b9b3</T>
      <T n="text">0xA8A60739<!--Once the industrial heart of Nordhaven, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Iverstad</font></b> has transformed into a vibrant neighborhood for ambitious Sims. Old factories have been reborn as chic living spaces, and new developments are sprouting up everywhere. Explore local gems like <b><font color='#199C2C'>Terra-Potta Pottery</font></b>, where you can get your hands dirty creating masterpieces in a cherished studio. Express yourself at the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Spilled Neon</font></b> Tattoo Parlor, known for its unique designs from the city's most creative tattoo artists. And perhaps venture into the dark alley at night—rumor has it there’s nothing but <i>perfectly legitimate</i> secrets to uncover!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_World_Slide3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:19cb7364b514b9b2</T>
      <T n="text">0xA4AB8617<!--Step into the past with <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gammelvik</font></b>, Nordhaven's oldest district, where cobbled streets and classic architecture tell tales of history. Enjoy leisurely bike rides and soak in the local culture. Stop by <b><font color='#199C2C'>Koffieboon</font></b>, a charming café where you can sip coffee, browse books, and enjoy a cozy afternoon. Experience warm nights filled with music at the local lounge, <b><font color='#199C2C'>The Rouge Note</font></b>. For art enthusiasts, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Konst Modern</font></b> offers a newly renovated museum featuring state-of-the-art facilities for pottery, painting, and woodworking—making it a hub for creativity and community learning. <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gammelvik</font></b> invites you to take life at your own pace.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_World_Slide4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:19cb7364b514b9b5</T>
      <T n="text">0x43D53C1B<!--Throughout the week, Sims can participate in exciting <b><font color='#199C2C'>Hobby Meetup Events</font></b> happening at the dedicated meetup location in each neighborhood:\n\n• Between <b><font color='#199C2C'>Koffieboon</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>The Rouge Note</font></b> in <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gammelvik</font></b>\n• Next to <b><font color='#199C2C'>The Old Foundry</font></b> in <b><font color='#199C2C'>Iverstad</font></b>\n\nThese events offer a chance for Sims to enjoy their hobbies, connect with others who share their interests, make new friends, learn new skills, and enjoy fun activities together in a lively, community-driven environment.\nInteract with the <b>Hobby Meetup Signs</b> at the meetup locations in each neighborhood to gain more information about the different meetup events.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
